        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 15. (a–e) Hapalotremus martinorum, female paratype (MLP 19153). (a) Carapace, dorsal view. (b) Sternum, ventral view. (c) Abdomen, dorsal view. (d) Abdomen, ventral view. (e) Abdomen, lateral view. Scale bar: 5 mm. Photos: Nelson Ferretti." ;
